{"tid":1647982,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"出黎嘅時候要美國旗呀！！！","createTime":"2019-10-12T03:54:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T16:33:19.000Z","uid":4028,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c903ad113c7a627005641d0fa783fbb3c6ad2165","tid":1647982,"uid":4028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T03:54:56.000Z","msg":"Trump講左話香港示威少左人，係咪真係少左人呀？唔係，因為遍地開花分散左人，但人數依然係多！<br />\n如果遍地開花，區區都有美國旗，咁就show到全香港都需要美國幫手<br />\n<br />\nTrump之前屌緊NBA球員唔愛國，講國家壞話，如果我地擁護美國，揮動美國旗，將美國戰線中興！！！<br />\n<br />\n美國旗係國際戰線嘅最大武器呀！！！"},{"pid":"13fe7a71d79fce2ed0a5c0d683c4d95893d73b69","tid":1647982,"uid":4028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T03:56:29.000Z","msg":"推呀，十八區開花再加美國旗，將戰線融合再進化！"},{"pid":"7058607e769d8cf485780612b0e8da36e4ca70be","tid":1647982,"uid":4028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T03:59:06.000Z","msg":"推爆佢！大家出黎要美國旗！"},{"pid":"2a788514c6761ec8026fbe8112aac9737bdb61a6","tid":1647982,"uid":56983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T04:01:12.000Z","msg":"有用，推呀！<br />\n侵侵都提曬水，我地要識得進化"},{"pid":"857d74c9d996770d4ad88fe9474b2f352f35ca44","tid":1647982,"uid":41257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T04:04:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0512b5f96decd4884a4d3339edc70dc62377ed2d","tid":1647982,"uid":45556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T04:10:00.000Z","msg":"係咪有人講過要反轉美帝旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be00a2fe5587ee8feac95f26119b0610fe9c29f6","tid":1647982,"uid":4028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0512b5f96decd4884a4d3339edc70dc62377ed2d","tid":1647982,"uid":45556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T04:10:00.000Z","msg":"係咪有人講過要反轉美帝旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T04:11:48.000Z","msg":"點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji